TO HAVE SOMEBODY ♪

00:24.676 --> 00:27.984
♪ WHEN THE EDGE OF
SURRENDER'S IN SIGHT ♪

00:28.115 --> 00:30.769
♪ DON'T YOU WORRY

00:31.379 --> 00:34.164
♪ IT'S GONNA BE ALRIGHT ♪

00:36.949 --> 00:38.821
♪ CAUSE I'M ALWAYS READY

00:38.951 --> 00:42.303
