NUMBER OF THINGS.

16:34.036 --> 16:35.733
HIS NERVOUS SYSTEM, HIS
HEARING, HIS HEART--

16:35.864 --> 16:39.085
-I KNOW, I KNOW, I WENT OVER
EVERYTHING WITH THE DOCTOR.

16:40.086 --> 16:41.870
LANE, HE SUGGESTED WE
SHUT DOWN THE BEACHES

16:42.001 --> 16:42.958
AS A PRECAUTION.

16:44.046 --> 16:46.092
-NO, THE LAGOON APPEARS
TO BE THE ONLY AREA

16:46.222 --> 16:47.615
OF SIGNIFICANT CONTAMINATION.

16:47.745 --> 16:49.530
-ANY THEORIES ON HOW
IT GOT CONTAMINATED?

16:50.879 --> 16:52.533
-WELL, THERE'S A STORM
DRAIN ABOUT 20 FEET

16:52.663 --> 16:53.490
FROM THE ENTRANCE OF THE LAGOON.

16:54.143 --> 16:55.536
A LOT OF THE TIME
AFTER A HEAVY RAIN

16:55.666 --> 16:57.190
POLLUTERS WILL JUST
DUMP INTO A STORM DRAIN.

16:57.886 --> 16:59.453
THE RUNOFF CARRIES
IT OUT INTO THE BAY

16:59.583 --> 17:00.628
AND MAKES IT VIRTUALLY
IMPOSSIBLE FOR 'EM TO TRACE.

17:02.325 --> 17:04.327
-WELL, I PUT IN
A CALL TO THE EPA,

17:04.458 --> 17:06.502
THEY SAID THEY'D SEND OUT
A TEAM OF INVESTIGATORS.

17:06.634 --> 17:08.375
-YEAH? WELL, I WOULDN'T
COUNT TOO HEAVILY

17:08.505 --> 17:09.984
ON A BUNCH OF
GOVERNMENT BUREAUCRATS.

17:10.116 --> 17:11.551
THESE GUYS ARE
GONNA COME OUT HERE,

17:11.682 --> 17:12.857
THEY'RE GONNA ASK
A LOT OF QUESTIONS,

17:12.988 --> 17:14.511
THEY'RE GONNA TAKE
A LOT OF MEMOS,

17:14.642 --> 17:16.165
AND THEY'RE GONNA MOVE
ON TO THE NEXT CASE.

17:20.778 --> 17:22.737
HEY, TELL HOBIE, "HI."

17:23.867 --> 17:25.044
-I WILL.

17:26.219 --> 17:30.049
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

17:40.233 --> 17:42.496
[CAR REVVING]

17:51.505 --> 17:52.288
-LANE: JEFF?

17:52.419 --> 17:53.420
-YEAH.

17:53.550 --> 17:54.899
-LANE BRODY.

17:59.469 --> 18:00.470
[DOOR BANGING]

18:01.080 --> 18:03.038
NICE TO FINALLY ASSOCIATE
A FACE WITH THE VOICE.

18:03.169 --> 18:05.432
-SAME HERE, IT'S A
PRIVILEGE TO MEET YOU.

18:05.562 --> 18:07.216
I WISH I HAD HALF YOUR GUTS.

18:07.347 --> 18:09.088
-AW, HELL, YOU'RE THE ONE
THAT'S RISKING HIS CAREER.

18:10.089 --> 18:11.525
-THIS WILL GET YOU INSIDE.

18:11.655 --> 18:12.830
YOU'RE A COMPUTER TECHNICIAN.

18:13.396 --> 18:14.745
I'VE GOT YOUR GEAR IN THE TRUNK.

18:15.529 --> 18:16.660
-OKAY.

18:20.664 --> 18:24.538
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

18:29.891 --> 18:31.893
-MMM, GOOD.

18:32.023 --> 18:33.242
-DAD, DON'T MAKE ME EAT THAT.

18:33.373 --> 18:34.678
-COME ON.

18:34.809 --> 18:36.115
-DAD, PLEASE, IT
TASTES LIKE TURPENTINE.

18:36.245 --> 18:37.464
-COME ON, PAL,
YOU'RE GONNA SPILL IT.

18:37.594 --> 18:38.856
COME ON, OPEN UP.

18:38.987 --> 18:40.423
AH, THAT A BOY.

18:40.554 --> 18:44.775
-EW, HOW LONG DID THE
DOCTOR SAY I'D BE SICK?

18:45.689 --> 18:46.864
-A COUPLE OF DAYS.

18:47.865 --> 18:49.998
BUT YOU'LL GET BETTER A LOT
FASTER IF YOU GET SOME REST.

18:51.478 --> 18:52.783
-BUT I'M NOT TIRED.

18:52.914 --> 18:54.655
-[LAUGHING] NOT MUCH.

18:55.264 --> 18:56.744
[SMOOCHES] COME ON.

18:58.180 --> 19:00.574
GET SOME SLEEP, I LOVE YOU.

19:01.575 --> 19:02.489
-HOBIE: DAD?

19:03.446 --> 19:04.708
-YEAH?

19:04.839 --> 19:05.970
-COULD YOU READ ME A STORY?

19:07.450 --> 19:09.844
-YEAH, SURE, WHICH ONE?

19:10.627 --> 19:11.672
-YOU CHOOSE.

19:16.416 --> 19:18.287
-MITCH: OKAY, LET'S SEE.

19:22.813 --> 19:24.206
REMEMBER THIS ONE?

19:27.383 --> 19:28.210
TOO SCARY?

19:28.950 --> 19:29.820
-NO WAY.

19:29.951 --> 19:30.865
-OKAY.

19:33.172 --> 19:34.129
SCOOT OVER, PAL.

19:38.481 --> 19:39.308
YOU READY?

19:40.962 --> 19:43.747
"THE GHOST IN THE CLOSET.

19:45.575 --> 19:48.012
"IT WAS A COLD AND DREARY NIGHT.

19:49.100 --> 19:50.711
"THERE WAS A KNOCK ON THE DOOR.

19:50.841 --> 19:52.365
[KNOCKING]

19:53.061 --> 19:55.759
"A HOWLING DOG COULD BE
HEARD IN THE BACKGROUND.

19:55.890 --> 19:57.935
[HOWLING]

19:59.067 --> 20:01.809
"THERE WAS A CRACK OF THUNDER
AND A FLASH OF LIGHTNING.

20:02.505 --> 20:04.507
[CRACKLING]

20:06.466 --> 20:08.294
"THE KNOCK CAME
AGAIN ON THE DOOR.

20:08.946 --> 20:10.383
[KNOCKING]

20:10.513 --> 20:13.386
"SLOWLY, THE DOOR
HANDLE TURNED."

20:13.951 --> 20:14.996
[CREAKING]

20:15.126 --> 20:18.086
[MYSTERIOUS MUSIC]

20:39.803 --> 20:41.544
-THIS WAY.

20:41.675 --> 20:43.329
-WAIT, WAIT A MINUTE, ONE
THING THAT WE HAVEN'T DISCUSSED,

20:43.851 --> 20:45.592
THE GUARDS ARE GONNA CHECK MY
BRIEFCASE WHEN I'M LEAVING.

20:45.722 --> 20:48.029
