OUT WITH THE DOCUMENTS?

20:49.422 --> 20:50.988
-THROUGH THE FENCE.

20:52.294 --> 20:55.123
[KEYS BEEPING]

20:57.995 --> 21:00.824
[MYSTERIOUS MUSIC]

21:15.404 --> 21:18.320
I'M SURE YOU'LL FIND
AMPLE EVIDENCE OF ABUSE.

21:19.887 --> 21:21.889
[PAPERS RUSTLING]
[VOICES MURMURING]

21:22.019 --> 21:23.238
I'LL CHECK IT OUT.

21:23.369 --> 21:26.546
[MYSTERIOUS MUSIC]

21:32.073 --> 21:33.466
-THIS IS UNBELIEVABLE,
IF YOU'RE GONNA--

21:33.596 --> 21:35.163
[BASHING] AHH.

21:35.294 --> 21:37.818
[MYSTERIOUS MUSIC]

21:49.699 --> 21:51.179
[MITCH SIGHING]

21:55.618 --> 22:00.754
-"STEP BY STEP, BRANDON
WALKED DOWN THE STAIRS.

22:01.407 --> 22:04.888
"SUDDENLY, A GHOST
FLEW OUT OF THE CLOSET,

22:05.019 --> 22:07.543
"AND HE CALLED, 'MOM, MOM.'"

22:09.980 --> 22:12.766
[MYSTERIOUS MUSIC]

22:31.132 --> 22:32.873
[KEYS BEEPING]

22:42.578 --> 22:46.103
[MITCH BREATHING DEEPLY]

22:47.931 --> 22:48.976
[SMOOCHES]

22:59.290 --> 23:01.597
[MYSTERIOUS MUSIC]

23:01.728 --> 23:03.425
[LANE GROANING]

23:06.428 --> 23:08.256
[MYSTERIOUS MUSIC]

23:12.565 --> 23:15.524
[FRANTIC MUSIC]

23:25.012 --> 23:27.928
[SPLASHING]

23:39.679 --> 23:44.814
[MYSTERIOUS MUSIC]

