24:19.893 --> 24:21.024
-MITCH: COMING.

24:28.292 --> 24:30.033
HEY, CAPTAIN.

24:30.164 --> 24:32.819
-HEY, MITCH, LOOK, I'M SORRY
TO BOTHER YOU, HOW'S HOBIE?

24:32.949 --> 24:34.690
-OH, HE'S OKAY, HE'S SLEEPING.

24:35.386 --> 24:36.866
-GOOD, GOOD.

24:36.997 --> 24:38.172
MITCH, THERE'S BEEN AN ACCIDENT

24:38.302 --> 24:39.303
AT THE TRANSICON
INDUSTRIES' PLANT.

24:39.434 --> 24:40.653
-WHAT HAPPENED?

24:40.783 --> 24:42.132
-ONE OF THE
PIPELINES WAS BLOWN,

24:42.263 --> 24:44.134
OVER 100,000 GALLONS
OF TOXIC CHEMICALS

24:44.265 --> 24:45.484
SPILLED INTO THE STORM CHANNEL.

24:46.310 --> 24:47.616
SHOULD REACH THE
BAY ABOUT SUNUP,

24:47.747 --> 24:48.704
WE'VE GOTTA CLOSE
DOWN ALL THE BEACHES

24:48.835 --> 24:49.966
FROM PALOS VERDES TO POINT DUME.

24:50.097 --> 24:51.446
-OKAY, I'M ON IT.

24:52.795 --> 24:54.275
-NOW, MITCH, I'VE ALREADY
TALKED TO THE CHIEF.

24:54.405 --> 24:55.494
WE'RE COORDINATING
WITH THE COAST GUARD.

24:59.498 --> 25:01.151
-HOW THE HELL DID THIS HAPPEN?

25:01.282 --> 25:02.718
-ACCORDING TO THE POLICE,

25:02.849 --> 25:03.937
LANE BRODY WAS TRYING
TO SABOTAGE THE PLANT.

25:08.376 --> 25:09.899
-WHAT?

25:10.030 --> 25:12.772
-THEY FIGURE HIS EXPLOSIVES
DETONATED PREMATURELY.

25:13.903 --> 25:16.776
MITCH, HE'S IN A COMA,
HE'S FIGHTING FOR HIS LIFE.

25:16.906 --> 25:20.693
[MELANCHOLY MUSIC]

25:21.432 --> 25:24.740
[MACHINES BEEPING]

25:37.361 --> 25:38.580
-HEY, BUDDY.

25:40.408 --> 25:41.540
IT'S ME, MITCH.

25:47.241 --> 25:49.460
I GUESS YOU WERE RIGHT
ABOUT NEEDING BACKUP, HUH?

25:53.290 --> 25:54.944
WHAT HAPPENED, MAN?

25:55.989 --> 25:57.468
I DON'T KNOW WHO
TO BELIEVE HERE.

26:01.995 --> 26:05.999
LANE, IF YOU TALK TO
ME, I CAN HELP YOU.

26:12.179 --> 26:14.747
OKAY, PAL, JUST REST EASY.

26:16.618 --> 26:17.663
DON'T YOU WORRY.

26:19.665 --> 26:20.753
WE'LL NAIL THESE GUYS.

26:21.492 --> 26:24.365
[MACHINES BEEPING]

26:32.155 --> 26:34.723
