28:39.239 --> 28:41.197
WHEN THE BEACHES
WILL BE OPENED.

28:42.024 --> 28:44.418
I CAN'T SPECULATE ON THE
EXTENT OF THE DAMAGES.

28:44.548 --> 28:45.724
LET'S JUST SAY
THEY'RE NOT GOOD.

28:45.854 --> 28:46.812
[BUZZING]

28:46.942 --> 28:48.161
OKAY, THANK YOU FOR CALLING.

28:48.291 --> 28:49.771
[BUZZING]

28:49.902 --> 28:51.425
BAYWATCH.

28:51.555 --> 28:52.469
YEAH.

28:53.514 --> 28:54.645
OKAY.

28:57.692 --> 28:59.389
UH-HUH.

28:59.520 --> 29:03.437
-ALRIGHT, WHAT DO WE KNOW
ABOUT TRANSICON INDUSTRIES?

29:04.003 --> 29:05.265
IS THIS THEIR FIRST SPILL?

29:05.918 --> 29:07.789
-WHAT DIFFERENCE
DOES THAT MAKE, MITCH?

29:07.920 --> 29:10.574
IT WASN'T INTENTIONAL,
IT WAS LANE.

29:10.705 --> 29:12.925
HE TOOK THE LAW RIGHT
INTO HIS OWN HANDS.

29:13.055 --> 29:15.362
-LANE WENT THERE TO GET
EVIDENCE TO BUST THESE GUYS.

29:15.928 --> 29:18.321
THERE'S NO WAY HE'D
INTENTIONALLY CREATE
A TOXIC SPILL.

29:18.452 --> 29:20.584
-AND THERE'S NO
WAY THAT TRANSICON

29:20.715 --> 29:23.805
IS GOING TO INTENTIONALLY
BLOW UP ITS OWN FACILITY.

29:23.936 --> 29:25.546
-COME ON, YOU WORKED WITH
LANE BRODY FOR 10 YEARS.

29:25.676 --> 29:27.809
-MITCH, THE POINT IS WE
HAVEN'T SEEN ANY EVIDENCE

29:27.940 --> 29:30.333
TO EVEN SUGGEST THAT
LANE WAS SET UP.

29:30.464 --> 29:32.031
NOT THAT I'M RULING THAT
OUT AS A POSSIBILITY,

29:32.161 --> 29:34.729
BUT THE FACT REMAINS LANE
WAS TRAINED IN THE NAVY

29:34.860 --> 29:36.035
TO USE EXPLOSIVES.

29:36.165 --> 29:37.558
-THE LAB JUST GAVE
A POSITIVE I.D.

29:37.688 --> 29:39.429
ON THE SUBSTANCE WE
FOUND IN THE LAGOON.

29:39.560 --> 29:42.302
IT'S CALLED AZ-47,
AND IT'S A PESTICIDE.

29:42.911 --> 29:44.695
OR I SHOULD SAY IT
WAS A PESTICIDE.

29:44.826 --> 29:45.871
-WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

29:46.480 --> 29:48.743
-IT'S BEEN BANNED BY THE
DEPARTMENT OF AGRICULTURE.

29:48.874 --> 29:51.746
IT HASN'T BEEN PRODUCED IN
THIS COUNTRY FOR OVER 15 YEARS.

29:51.877 --> 29:53.530
-15 YEARS?

29:54.096 --> 29:55.837
-AND ALL OF A SUDDEN IT
ENDS UP IN OUR BACKYARD?

29:56.446 --> 29:58.274
-AND OF COURSE, AT THIS
POINT, IT'S ALMOST ACADEMIC,

29:58.405 --> 30:00.276
I MEAN, WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO
CLEAN UP THE ENTIRE SHORELINE

30:00.407 --> 30:01.408
AFTER THIS SPILL, ANYWAY.

30:01.538 --> 30:03.932
[PHONE RINGING]

30:04.803 --> 30:06.065
-BUCHANNON.

30:07.196 --> 30:09.633
YES, YEAH, I'M THERE.

30:11.287 --> 30:12.898
HE'S OUT OF THE COMA.

30:13.028 --> 30:17.685
[BRIGHT MUSIC]

30:19.078 --> 30:21.297
-WOMAN: THERE YOU
GO, WALK THE STAIRS,

30:21.428 --> 30:23.256
JUST TAKE YOUR TIME.

30:26.259 --> 30:27.477
-HI.

30:27.608 --> 30:29.262
-YOUR FRIEND IS
A VERY LUCKY MAN.

30:29.392 --> 30:30.872
-CAN WE SEE HIM?
-SURE, IN A MINUTE.

30:31.003 --> 30:32.265
HE'S WITH HIS PRIEST RIGHT NOW.

30:32.395 --> 30:33.701
-GO AHEAD, I'LL WAIT.

30:34.310 --> 30:35.442
-HIS PRIEST?

30:36.225 --> 30:37.531
LANE'S NOT CATHOLIC.

30:37.661 --> 30:38.532
-HE'S NOT?

30:44.581 --> 30:46.018
[DOOR CRASHING]

30:47.846 --> 30:51.893
[GRUNTING]
[FRANTIC MUSIC]

30:54.330 --> 30:55.462
[GRUNTING]

30:55.592 --> 30:57.899
[SMASHING]

31:10.259 --> 31:11.608
[BANGING]

31:17.049 --> 31:18.615
-HE'S STILL ALIVE.

31:18.746 --> 31:21.880
-[MOANING]
PLAYA DEL SOL.

31:22.489 --> 31:23.446
-WHAT?

31:23.577 --> 31:28.408
-TRANSICON, PLAYA DEL SOL.

31:29.496 --> 31:30.410
-YOU HANG IN THERE, BUDDY.

31:31.324 --> 31:32.673
YOU TAKE CARE OF HIM, ALRIGHT?

31:32.803 --> 31:34.066
HANG IN THERE.

31:40.072 --> 31:42.944
[MYSTERIOUS MUSIC]

31:50.821 --> 31:52.127
-HEY.

31:52.258 --> 31:53.694
-HEY, OH, I GOT A
CALL FROM GARNER.

31:54.260 --> 31:57.219
TURNS OUT THE PRIEST IS NOT
COOPERATING WITH THE POLICE.

31:57.350 --> 31:58.742
HE WON'T EVEN GIVE HIS NAME.

31:59.830 --> 32:01.354
-WHAT DO YOU THINK
PLAYA DEL SOL MEANS?

32:01.876 --> 32:03.051
-THE AREA AROUND THE LAGOON

32:03.182 --> 32:04.618
USED TO BE CALLED
PLAYA DEL SOL.

32:04.748 --> 32:06.359
BEFORE THEY BUILT THOSE
MILLION DOLLAR HOMES,

32:06.489 --> 32:07.360
IT WAS A LANDFILL.

32:08.013 --> 32:08.883
-WHAT'S THAT?

32:09.014 --> 32:10.624
[PAPER RUSTLING]

32:11.451 --> 32:12.713
-THAT'S WHAT THEY
GOT FROM LANE.

32:12.843 --> 32:14.367
THE NURSE CALLED IT IN.

32:16.282 --> 32:18.110
-WHAT IS THIS, IT'S SOME
KIND OF A CODE, WHAT'S IT FOR?

32:18.240 --> 32:21.287
-I DON'T KNOW, THAT'S ALL
SHE WROTE, JUST THOSE NUMBERS.

32:22.027 --> 32:23.680
-WELL DO YOU THINK THIS HAS
SOMETHING TO DO WITH TRANSICON?

32:23.811 --> 32:24.768
-YEAH.

32:26.074 --> 32:27.380
-WELL, DID YOU
TELL THE POLICE?

32:28.642 --> 32:29.686
-NO.

32:31.688 --> 32:33.168
-I REALLY HOPE THAT
YOU'RE NOT THINKING ABOUT

32:33.299 --> 32:35.083
CONDUCTING THIS
INVESTIGATION ON YOUR OWN.

32:36.519 --> 32:39.174
-SHAUNI, BEFORE THE POLICE
GET A SEARCH WARRANT TOGETHER

32:39.740 --> 32:41.220
THOSE FILES COULD BE DESTROYED.

32:41.350 --> 32:43.352
-MITCH, THAT'S CRAZY!

32:43.483 --> 32:45.050
NO WAY, FORGET IT,
YOU'RE NOT DOING IT.

32:46.573 --> 32:47.530
AT LEAST NOT WITHOUT ME.

32:47.661 --> 32:49.141
-NO, YOU CAN FORGET THAT.

32:49.271 --> 32:51.056
-NO, I WON'T FORGET IT!

32:51.186 --> 32:53.623
LOOK, LANE IS SOMEBODY
THAT I ADMIRE VERY MUCH.

32:54.233 --> 32:56.365
AND RIGHT NOW IT'S HIS
WORD AGAINST TRANSICON'S.

32:56.496 --> 32:58.889
HE CAN STILL BE SENT TO
PRISON FOR THAT BOMBING

32:59.020 --> 33:01.370
UNLESS WE PROVE THAT
THEY FRAMED HIM.

33:01.501 --> 33:03.155
AND YOU WANT TO
KNOW SOMETHING ELSE?

33:03.285 --> 33:05.722
I AM REALLY GETTING SICK
AND TIRED OF COMPANIES

33:05.853 --> 33:08.551
LIKE TRANSICON DUMPING
THEIR CRAP IN MY WATER.

33:08.682 --> 33:10.118
ENOUGH IS ENOUGH!

33:10.249 --> 33:11.946
IF WE DON'T STAND UP
TO THEM, WHO WILL?

33:12.947 --> 33:14.470
-SOUNDS LIKE I GOT A BACKUP.

33:15.080 --> 33:16.124
-YOU'RE DAMN RIGHT YOU DO.

33:16.255 --> 33:19.823
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

33:33.011 --> 33:35.709
[CLICKING]

33:35.839 --> 33:39.060
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

33:48.852 --> 33:51.464
[CLICKING]

33:55.120 --> 33:56.686
-HERE.

33:58.645 --> 34:01.561
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

34:50.304 --> 34:53.351
[BEEPING]
[DOOR OPENING]

34:54.788 --> 34:58.792
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

35:20.379 --> 35:23.556
[BEEPING]

35:27.821 --> 35:29.823
[DOOR CREAKING]

35:40.138 --> 35:41.400
-WHY DON'T YOU TAKE THESE, HUH?

35:41.530 --> 35:44.664
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

35:54.891 --> 35:55.892
I GOT IT.

35:58.199 --> 35:59.331
PLAYA DEL SOL.

36:05.163 --> 36:06.120
LANE WAS RIGHT.

36:06.990 --> 36:07.991
-WELL, IS THIS ALL WE NEED?

36:08.122 --> 36:09.123
-YEAH.

36:09.254 --> 36:10.342
-GOOD, LET'S GET OUT OF HERE.

36:10.864 --> 36:12.431
[FILING CABINET CLOSES]

36:20.265 --> 36:21.309
[DOOR CLOSING]

36:28.969 --> 36:30.536
-I'LL TAKE THAT BAG.

36:31.798 --> 36:34.627
YOU'RE IN NO POSITION TO
RESIST, AND I WON'T ASK AGAIN.

36:37.673 --> 36:39.022
-HANDS UP.

36:40.546 --> 36:42.287
-I'M SURE YOU HAVE AN
EXPLANATION FOR THIS.

36:43.592 --> 36:45.203
-WE'RE FRIENDS OF LANE BRODY.

36:45.855 --> 36:47.161
-SHAUNI: WE KNOW
YOU TRIED TO KILL HIM.

36:48.554 --> 36:52.035
WE ALSO KNOW THAT 15
